data.description: Cozy, neutral, absolutely adorable! This 3 bedroom 2 bathroom home located just outside city limits has plenty of life left and room to grow with you. This home has a converted bonus room or dining room along with indoor laundry/mud room, fresh interior paint throughout, and room to entertain! Brand new roof, replaced October 2023. The kitchen has ample cabinets and counter top space and even room to add an island for more space if needed. The primary bedroom has an en suite and large closet that is a perfect blank canvas for your style. Tile and wood-look laminate flooring throughout the main living areas. If grilling is your jam, then this backyard is for you! Large concrete grilling patio or lounging area right off the screened-in patio to enjoy all weather. With over half an acre, a fully fenced backyard, and trees as your backyard neighbor, you are guaranteed to love all of the privacy this home has to offer. No HOA, no city taxes, and totally ready for you to call this place your home.
